OL,3,CThe trailblazing trans woman who made
OL,4,CWales her home after being outed
OL,6,FA trailblazing transgender woman, who
OL,7,Ffound refuge in a small Welsh border
OL,8,Ftown after she was publicly outed by
OL,9,Fthe press, is the subject of a new
OL,10,Fexhibition in Hay-on-Wye.
OL,12,FEvery morning, April Ashley would wake
OL,13,Fup praying she was a girl.
OL,15,FBorn George Jamieson in Liverpool in
OL,16,F1935, April lived most of her early
OL,17,Flife unhappy through confusion over
OL,18,Fher gender, and a rocky home life.
