OL,3,CThe trailblazing trans woman who made
OL,4,CWales her home after being outed
OL,6,FApril travelled to Casablanca, Morocco
OL,7,Fto become Dr Georges Burou's ninth
OL,8,Fpatient at his clinic, having saved up
OL,9,Fthe money working at Le Carrousel
OL,10,Fnightclub in Paris.
OL,12,FAfter returning to the UK, she became
OL,13,Fa well known model and actress, even
OL,14,Fappearing in British Vogue.
OL,16,FHowever, less than a year after
OL,17,Ftransitioning, she would become the
OL,18,Fcentre of a media frenzy, which
OL,19,Fstarted when a friend sold her story
OL,20,Fto The Sunday People newspaper and she
OL,21,Fwas outed publicly.
