OL,3,CThe trailblazing trans woman who made
OL,4,CWales her home after being outed
OL,6,FThe town which April once called home,
OL,7,Fis now the setting of an exhibition
OL,8,Fabout her life.
OL,10,FMari Fforde, Exhibition Curator and
OL,11,FLearning Manager at Hay Castle, said:
OL,12,F"April was a well- known part of the
OL,13,Fcommunity here in Hay, and we were
OL,14,Fkeen to tell her story in a way that
OL,15,Fexpresses the fondness with which she
OL,16,Fis remembered as well as conveying the
OL,17,Fimportant part she played in
OL,18,Ftransgender history in the UK and
OL,19,Facross the world.
