OL,3,CThe trailblazing trans woman who made
OL,4,CWales her home after being outed
OL,6,F"The idea with the exhibition is to
OL,7,Fshow the two sides of her life ` one
OL,8,Froom looks at the public face of the
OL,9,Fmodel who was outed by The Sunday
OL,10,FPeople in 1961 and whose image was all
OL,11,Fover the headlines during her divorce
OL,12,Fand the other explores her private
OL,13,Flife in Hay and the person behind the
OL,14,Fheadlines."
